params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" M_CUST.CUST_CD, " +" M_CUST.CUST_ANAME " +"FROM " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" And M_CUST.CUST_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT, " +" M_ITEM.UNIT_QTY_TYP, " +" M_ITEM.MRP_ODR_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM_SPEC, " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_NAME, " +" M_WH.PLANT_CD " +"FROM " +" M_CUST_BASE, " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST_BASE.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.SHIP_WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD"

"SELECT " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_NAME, " +" M_WH.PLANT_CD " +"FROM " +" M_CUST_BASE, " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST_BASE.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.SHIP_WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_SALES_PLAN(SALES_PLAN_CD, COMPANY_CD, CUST_CD, CUST_ITEM_CD, DLV_LOC_CD, PLN_STR_DATE, PLN_END_DATE, TERM_DAYS, PLN_TERM_TYP, PLN_QTY, ADD_TO_OD_FLG, PLN_QTY_REMAIN) " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"

"SELECT " +" SALES_PLAN_CD " +"FROM " +" T_SALES_PLAN " +"WHERE " +" T_SALES_PLAN.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND T_SALES_PLAN.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND T_SALES_PLAN.CUST_ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_SALES_PLAN.DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND T_SALES_PLAN.DLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND(? BETWEEN T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_STR_DATE AND T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_END_DATE " +" OR ? BETWEEN T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_STR_DATE AND T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_END_DATE " +" OR T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_STR_DATE BETWEEN ? AND ? " +" OR T_SALES_PLAN.PLN_END_DATE BETWEEN ? AND ?)"
